# Go Conventions

## Tooling
- Format: `make fmt` (gofumpt + goimports)
- Lint: `make lint` (see [.golangci.yml](mdc:.golangci.yml))
- Audit: `make audit` (all checks)

## Code Patterns
- Errors: Always check (errcheck enabled)
- Complexity: Max cyclomatic 15
- Interfaces: Define in consuming package

## Key Types
- Platform: [model/platform.go](mdc:internal/model/platform.go) (ClaudeCode, Cursor, Codex)
- Skill: [model/skill.go](mdc:internal/model/skill.go)
- Parser: [parser/parser.go](mdc:internal/parser/parser.go)
